OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWidespread
OL,6,Fhazy sunshine this evening with winds
OL,7,Feasing, then dry and mostly fine
OL,8,Fovernight. Chance of a few localised
OL,9,Fmist or fog patches developing inland
OL,10,Flate in the night and becoming rather
OL,11,Fchilly by morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FGenerally dry and warm with
OL,14,Fplenty of hazy sunshine, although
OL,15,Fbriefly cloudier at times with a risk
OL,16,Fof showers, perhaps turning thundery
OL,17,Fby the evening. Locally breezy in
OL,18,Fcoastal areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
